[zanshin_alerts://<name>]
api_key = Use Zanshin Portal to create a API key and enter it here.
organization_id = Organization ID (UUID) of the organization that will get the alerts
scan_target_ids = Optional comma-separated list of Scan Target IDs (UUID). Leave blank to get alerts from all Scan Targets accessible using the API key and Organization ID provided

[zanshin_following_alerts://<name>]
api_key = Use Zanshin Portal to create a API key and enter it here.
organization_id = Organization ID (UUID) of the organization that will get the alerts
following_ids = Optional comma-separated list of Following IDs (UUID). Leave blank to get alerts from all Following accessible using the API key and Organization ID provided